description:
ANN highlights the gathering that brought together over 400 Adventist World Church leaders for the 2023 Spring Meeting themed "I Will Go: Be His Witness".

This week, ANN also takes a look at the new podcast that aims to rekindle the missionary zeal among Adventists worldwide. ADRA assists cyclone victims in Vanuatu and provides shelter to families in need. Hundreds of Adventist communicators, digital evangelists, and influencers gather for GAiN Chiapas.

Watch as ANN highlights these stories and reports on other news from around the world. 

For more Adventist news, subscribe to our Youtube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit adventist.news
